  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Slice the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into discs, approx. 1cm thick</p>",
