    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> potato discs</strong> to a baking tray, drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, then season generously with <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-30 min or until the potatoes are cooked through and crispy – these are your <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong></p>",
